description: Omar is back!... and we must say he puts on quite the show for us this time! After some great comments from some of his admirers, as well as his interest to 'give us a second show', we took him up on his offer and he did deliver. He sports a brand new tattoo this time as well as a new attitude that we really like. And we certainly can't forget to mention that he's been continuing his hard work at the gym. It shows.Watch Omar tease us in two different scenes before releasing his pent-up energy.
title: Omar
